## ğŸ“– Bot Usage

### For Users

1. Start bot with `/start`
1. Add your Telegram account via **ğŸ“± Accounts â†’ â• Add Account**
1. Enter phone number â†’ receive code â†’ verify
1. Click **ğŸ“ Report**
1. Paste target username/link
1. Choose report type
1. Choose how many reports
1. All your accounts report simultaneously!

### For Admin

- **Admin Panel** â†’ Add tokens to users
- **Set Report Text** â†’ Override the auto-generated text for all reports
- View stats, manage accounts

### For Owner

- Unlimited tokens by default
- Promote/demote users to admin
- Ban/unban users
- Give unlimited tokens to any user
- All admin capabilities

